Package: vastRai
Title: AI-Assisted Translation Between Narrative Theories and VAST Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Luebber", "Finn", email = "f.luebber2@uni-luebeck.de",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0893-2120"))
    )
Description: Provides tools for translating between narrative theory paragraphs and
    Visual Argument Structure Tool (VAST) models. Generates structured prompts for
    large language models to parse narrative text into VAST model specifications
    (JSON), and converts that JSON into vastR model code. Includes theory
    underspecification assessment based on the Indicators for Theoretical Rigor
    checklist.
